Author: ChubbieToad
Text: Recognizing that your behaviors aren't normal is good. Some times I get to the point where I think this stuff is normal and I don't realize it, that's when things get super scary

Author: nodamncatnodamncradl
Text: do you have a new stress in your life right now? If you feel out of control and like you are using behaviours that you don't like the feeling of, you might be experiencing coping mechanisms/compulsive stress response. just a thought. If that sounds familiar I encourage you to google mental health resources if you haven't already.
